A T4BS-style game scaffold built on BaseNative — five-letter battle of bullshit.

## Stack

- `@basenative/runtime` — signals + effects.
- `@basenative/keyboard` — on-screen QWERTY with letter-state colors.
- `@basenative/og-image` — server-rendered share cards.
- `@basenative/share` — share-result minting.
- `@basenative/auth-webauthn` — passkey auth.
- `@basenative/admin` — moderation queue.
- `@basenative/persist` — D1 helpers.

## Get going

```bash
pnpm install
bn dev
```

